&nbsp;
The United States reiterated "full support" to Israel against attacks by Iran, during a call between US Secretary of Defense Lloyd Austin and Israeli Defense Minister Yoav Gallant. It's a note from the U.S. Department of Defense. Lloyd, the Pentagon explains, "discussed regional urgent threats and reiterated the unwavering US support for Israel's defence." "Austin - we read in the note - made it clear that Israel can count on full American support in the defense of Israel against all attacks by Iran and its allies in the region."
